original: Johansson, Edvard Fredrik Torgny, jur. kand., direktör, Västervik, f. 15/ 7/05 i Sthlm av byggm. N. J. A. J. o. Hulda Charlotta Johansson. G. 42 m. Lillie Katarina Lindström. — Stud:ex. v. nya elem:sk. i Sthlm 24, jur. kand. v. Sthlms högsk. 30. Inneh. Västerviks jur. byrå fr. 39. Verkst. dir. i Gröndalens stenindustrier, Västervik, fr. 45.
translated: Johansson, Edvard Fredrik Torgny, LLB, director, Västervik, b. 15/7/05 in Stockholm to builder N. J. A. J. and Hulda Charlotta Johansson. Married in 1942 to Lillie Katarina Lindström. Graduated from upper secondary school in Stockholm in 1924 and obtained an LLB from Stockholm University in 1930. Owned the Västervik law firm from 1939. Executive director of Gröndalen Stone Industries, Västervik, from 1945.
